{"tid":1045111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「港漂」葉小姐： “香港應提供租金補貼，吸引人才！”","createTime":"2019-03-03T11:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T02:42:43.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8fb9b65473034ecf55b4b9d0b6395c8f671170","tid":1045111,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2019/02/16/b07a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F02%2F16%2Fb07a.jpg&h=88f5cf08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>租金補助可留「港漂」的心</strong><br />\n<br />\n在港工作一年半的葉小姐表示，「港漂」們一般會自行到招聘會中物色合適工作，政府也少作主導舉辦工作展覽。她指出，希望政府可多作中間人角色協助企業和畢業生配對工作，「我覺得可以分行業去舉行招聘會，讓想招人的公司和畢業生有機會接觸，也可多分享資訊給『港漂』們，讓他們更清楚香港企業招人的要求。」此外，租金高昂也是「港漂」們在港工作的問題之一，葉小姐指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">若政府可提供租金補助給「港漂」們將會更有效留住「港漂」人才</span></strong>，「租金補助不一定要有很多，但起碼這樣做會令學生們覺得政府支持『港漂』們留在香港工作。」"},{"pid":"ce12015d88dc9fe2c79fd2bf75c34a27a77ea45e","tid":1045111,"uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/02/16/OT1902160009.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F02%2F16%2FOT1902160009.htm&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=2c8160c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/02/16/OT1902160009.htm</a></ins>"},{"pid":"345b33bd33ccb63b1a303d5ddcaf372d3b2e1711","tid":1045111,"uid":142966,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"係勁既&quot;人才&quot;, 公司比埋宿舍你啦<br />\n洗鬼政府補貼"},{"pid":"fa44ea52111cd7012f3818c329c65eccaa970fdb","tid":1045111,"uid":227366,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"漂你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死撚返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161def7551caa08acd771cb